rComments: Some good teaching materials but relies too much on other people's models. Not very good at answering complex questions.

Good at communicating basic ideas based on her own experience as a junior consultant at McKinsey. Relies too much on abstract models. Struggles with more complex issues and specific questions. Tries to be helpful, but other EMBA profs tend to have more insights.
easy going class, was good insight into consulting world - has much experience and well connected
